# GSP/HTML copy default

For new or edited GSP/HTML templates in this repo:

1. Write UI copy directly in the template by default (plain text, labels, headings, help text, one-off page copy).
2. Do **not** add i18n keys to `grails-app/i18n/messages.properties` for one-off copy.
3. Extract text to `messages.properties` only when it is intentionally reusable (for example: shared button labels, repeated field headings, common flash/error text).
